{"title":"英雄碑","authors":["吕剑"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当人民的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从京城升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在彩云和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光中自由飞扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们的第一声礼炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊天动地向世界宣告，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共和国的开国大典，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当亲爱的毛泽东同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在红色天安门城楼庄严宣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中央人民政府第一号公告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当英雄的海陆空兵团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受自己领袖的检阅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并要继续无敌的南征西进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当全国人民欢迎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民政协的共同纲领，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人高举着它前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当工人阶级领队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民架桥铺路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向更高的美好的年代出发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当全世界的朋友兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们的伟大祖国祝贺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我们的领袖长寿举杯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们的开国元勋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你基石上撒上第一锨土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后对你落帽低首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们的开国元勋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣读“人民英雄们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永垂不朽”的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当每天黎明初升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵、露水散放香气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们开始了自己的工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当每一个大天白日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的建设生活在进行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市，田庄群相欢唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当每一个平静的夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们无忧无虑的安眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光照着人们对未来的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当敌人狼狈奔窜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跌入深坑，路入坟墓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后哀叫自己的覆亡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当战争贩子窃窃私语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想糟塌人民的花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人准备为斗争而献身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当全世界人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结成钢铁般和平营垒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫人民的幸福和文明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，向你敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你啊，英雄碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血的结晶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心的花岗石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花的结合体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你啊，英雄碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的冠冕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的号声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的史诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你啊，英雄碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们战斗的旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们胜利的旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们人民的旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你啊，英雄碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从地层生根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高耸入云空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽广有如全国海洋大陆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年十月一日—二日。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}